cf.lukasheinzl.lexing

Class TokenData

  • java.lang.Object
    • cf.lukasheinzl.lexing.TokenData

  • public class TokenData
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents a token template. It consists of a regular expression matching the token-value and the corresponding token type.
    Author:
    Lukas Heinzl
